nce-dies-season-3-finale.png?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=902%2C600 902w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/fire-country-vince-dies-season-3-finale.png?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=110%2C73 110w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/fire-country-vince-dies-season-3-finale.png?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=285%2C190 285w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/fire-country-vince-dies-season-3-finale.png?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=320%2C213 320w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/fire-country-vince-dies-season-3-finale.png?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=640%2C426 640w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/fire-country-vince-dies-season-3-finale.png?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=800%2C532 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" data-attachment-id=\"1235440117\" data-wp-size=\"nova_size__threebytwo_small_cropped\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOff Edwin’s visibly shocked reaction, she explained, “Helping people, righting wrongs, going to court…. I love it so much.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"630\" height=\"420\" src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png 630w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=200,133 200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=300,200 300w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=150,100 150w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=600,400 600w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=281,187 281w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=244,163 244w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=143,95 143w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=60,40 60w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=50,33 50w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=42,28 42w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=252,168 252w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=506,337 506w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=38,25 38w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=225,150 225w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=450,300 450w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=110,73 110w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=285,190 285w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-matty.png?resize=320,213 320w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhen Edwin reminded his missus that she had \u003cem\u003eretired\u003c/em\u003e from practicing law when Ellie died, she countered that it was “not because I wanted to” but so that she could tend to their suddenly parentless grandson and his needs. But Alfie, Edwin noted, still needs guardianship, and planning/making the teen’s dinners “is not how I pictured my golden years.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e“I understand that, but they’re \u003cem\u003emy\u003c/em\u003e golden years, too,” Matty argued. “You finished your career… and now I want to finish mine.”\n\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e“And if I say no?”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOuch. Those five little words took Matty aback. Us, too.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e“If you say no…?” she remarked. “I \u003cem\u003eneed\u003c/em\u003e this, Edwin. I cannot go back to being invisible” as a 75-year-old woman. To which Edwin shrugged, “You weren’t invisible to \u003cem\u003eme\u003c/em\u003e,” before walking away.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"620\" height=\"420\" src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png 620w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=200,135 200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=300,203 300w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=148,100 148w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=600,406 600w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=276,187 276w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=244,165 244w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=140,95 140w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=59,40 59w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=50,34 50w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=41,28 41w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=248,168 248w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=497,337 497w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=295,200 295w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=590,400 590w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=37,25 37w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=221,150 221w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=443,300 443w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=150,102 150w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=110,75 110w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=285,193 285w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/matlock-finale-fight-edwin.png?resize=320,217 320w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"can-madeline-and-edwin-s-marriage-survive\"\u003eCAN MADELINE AND EDWIN’S MARRIAGE SURVIVE?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eI really hate it when grandmom and grandad fight, so I brought my concerns about that Matty/Edwin heart-to-heart to \u003cem\u003eMatlock\u003c/em\u003e showrunner Jennie Snyder Urman.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e“I mean, it’s a 50-year marriage, right?” the EP noted. “So they have to figure it out, and that’s what I’m interested in. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e“But, how do you solve something in a long-term marriage when you say, ‘I want X and I want Y’ and they definitely don’t want X? Like, what happens?” asks Snyder Urman. The answer: “It’s the same thing as in a legal case when you get to a negotiable and you’re each non-negotiable. You \u003cem\u003estill\u003c/em\u003e have to negotiate. So I’m interested in seeing how they get through that and what it leads to.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAnd what it leads to when they \u003cem\u003edo\u003c/em\u003e eventually figure things out, Snyder Urman hints, “comes with things that cost Maddie, too, because you have to give things up in negotiations.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWant scoop on \u003cem\u003eMatlock\u003c/em\u003e, or for any other TV show? Shoot an email to \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"mailto:InsideLine@tvline.com\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eInsideLine@tvline.com\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, and your question may be answered via \u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/t/matts-inside-line/\"\u003eMatt’s Inside Line\u003c/a\u003e!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
